{{Otheruses|Blue}}
'''Rokna Blue''' was an extremely potent and [[Death/Legends|deadly]] narcotic that was extracted from a [[Rokna tree fungus|tree fungus]] on the forest [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]. The smallest amount&mdash;no more than a microgram&mdash;brought exquisite bliss which lasted for [[Standard hour/Legends|hours]] but was otherwise considered fatally [[Poison/Legends|poisonous]]. Another side effect of using "the [[Color/Legends|blue]]" was memory loss; one Rokna addict, [[Joreb Goss]], could not remember anything from more than a [[Standard year/Legends|year]] earlier.

It was popular in the time of the [[Black Fleet Crisis]], but later became rare outside of the [[Moddell sector/Legends|Moddell sector]] despite being cheaper than [[Glitterstim/Legends|glitterstim]].

